import React from 'react'
import {Container, Form } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const BrowseRestaurants = () => (
 <Container style = {{marginTop: 30}} >
    <Form>
        <Form.Field>
        <input placeholder='Search a restaurant' />
        </Form.Field>
    </Form>
 </Container>
  
)

export default BrowseRestaurants
